  "The demand from other industries": "",
  "The demand from end-users (consumers, government, exports) outside the inter-industry system": "",
  "The maximum production capacity": "",
  "Final demand is the portion of output consumed by households, government, or exported, as opposed to intermediate demand, which is consumed by other sectors in production.": "",
  "What is a 'Leontief inverse'?": "",
