  "A country has two sectors: agriculture (A) and manufacturing (M). Agriculture uses 0.2 of its own output and 0.3 of manufacturing output per dollar produced. Manufacturing uses 0.1 of agriculture and 0.4 of its own output. If external demand is $50 billion for A and $80 billion for M, write (I - C).": "",
