  "A trade analyst models exchange between 3 countries. Each country's spending is modeled as fractions of each other's goods. The exchange matrix E has columns summing to 1. She needs prices p such that Ep = p. This is equivalent to finding the eigenvector of E for which eigenvalue?": "",
